snippet.title: Pyramid - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Pyramid is a minimalist survival horror game.
We developped it for the confinement game jam.
Pyramid will be released in May 15th and will be available at www.dissidentstudio.fr.
All content : music and images are the property of Dissident Studio.
